Descriptions.Text:
Become an unstoppable storm of destructive force, striking all nearby enemies for {1} Physical damage over {2} sec. Deals reduced damage beyond {3} targets.

You are immune to movement impairing and loss of control effects, but can use defensive abilities and can avoid attacks.

{FFFFFFFF|Generates {4} Rage.}

A mighty blow with both weapons that deals a total of {1} Physical damage.

Raging Blow has a {2}% chance to instantly reset its own cooldown.

{FFFFFFFF|Generates {3} Rage.}

Charge to an enemy with your shield, dealing {1} Physical damage to it and {2} Physical damage to all enemies within {3} yards.

Also stuns the primary target for {4} sec.

{FFFFFFFF|Generates {5} Rage.}

Bash an enemy's skull, dealing {1} Physical damage.

Skullsplitter causes your Deep Wounds to expire instantly.

{FFFFFFFF|Generates {2} Rage.}

Throw a spear at the target location, dealing {1} Physical damage instantly and an additional {2} damage over {3} sec. Deals reduced damage beyond {4} targets.

Enemies hit are chained to the spear's location for the duration.

{FFFFFFFF|Generates {5} Rage.}

Unleashes a whirlwind of steel, striking all nearby enemies for {1} Physical damage. Deals reduced damage beyond {2} targets.

Causes your next {3} single-target melee attacks to strike up to {4} additional targets for {5}% damage.

{FFFFFFFF|Generates {6} Rage, plus an additional {7} per target hit.}
